lshw: lshw (Hardware Lister)
lshw:
lshw: lshw is a small tool to provide detailed information
lshw: on the hardware configuration of the machine. It can
lshw: report exact memory configuration, firmware version,
lshw: mainboard configuration, CPU version and speed, cache
lshw: configuration, bus speed, etc. on DMI-capable x86
lshw: systems and on some PowerPC machines (PowerMac G4 is
lshw: known to work).
lshw:
